{As a chess player who often gives chances left and right to the opponent, I
admire a lot those clean games where one player outplays the other. And the
finishing touch is executed beautifully with precise calculation.} 1. d4 Nf6 2.
c4 d6 3. Nc3 Nbd7 4. Nf3 e5 5. e4 g6 6. Be2 Bg7 7. O-O O-O 8. Be3 c6 9. d5 c5
